  "__TRANSLATE_77__": "the sandbox environment itself doesn't persist",
  "__TRANSLATE_78__": "Where Perplexity Computer genuinely wins",
  "__TRANSLATE_79__": "Zero setup.",
  "__TRANSLATE_80__": "No server, no configuration, no dependency management. Paste a goal, get a result. For non-technical users or one-off complex tasks this is a genuine edge.",
  "__TRANSLATE_81__": "Multi-model routing.",
  "__TRANSLATE_82__": "Automatically using the best model for each subtask — Gemini for deep research, Claude for reasoning, GPT-5.4 for long context — is something you'd have to build manually in Hermes.",
  "__TRANSLATE_83__": "Parallel sub-agents.",
  "__TRANSLATE_84__": "Running dozens of sub-agents simultaneously on separate sandboxes is powerful for research, competitive analysis, and data processing at scale.",
  "__TRANSLATE_85__": "Proprietary search index.",
  "__TRANSLATE_86__": "Perplexity's own search infrastructure (not reliant on third-party APIs) is consistently one of the better AI search products. It's built into every task.",
  "__TRANSLATE_87__": "400+ connectors out of the box.",
  "__TRANSLATE_88__": "The breadth of prebuilt OAuth integrations is wider than anything you'd set up yourself on a new Hermes install.",
